## GCP 前提リソース (Sprint 1 で 1 度だけ作成)

### 1. プロジェクト設定

```bash
export PROJECT_ID=ssw-public-prod
export REGION=asia-northeast1
gcloud config set project $PROJECT_ID
gcloud config set run/region $REGION

# 必要 API 有効化
gcloud services enable \
  run.googleapis.com \
  cloudbuild.googleapis.com \
  artifactregistry.googleapis.com \
  secretmanager.googleapis.com \
  discoveryengine.googleapis.com \
  aiplatform.googleapis.com \
  dlp.googleapis.com \
  cloudtrace.googleapis.com \
  iamcredentials.googleapis.com \
  vpcaccess.googleapis.com
```

### 2. Workload Identity Federation (GitHub Actions 用)

GitHub OIDC を信頼する Pool / Provider を作成:

```bash
gcloud iam workload-identity-pools create github \
  --location=global \
  --display-name="GitHub Actions"

gcloud iam workload-identity-pools providers create-oidc github-oidc \
  --workload-identity-pool=github \
  --location=global \
  --issuer-uri="https://token.actions.githubusercontent.com" \
  --attribute-mapping="google.subject=assertion.sub,attribute.repository=assertion.repository" \
  --attribute-condition="assertion.repository=='YOUR_GH_ORG/ssw-public'"

# Service Account 作成
gcloud iam service-accounts create ssw-deploy \
  --display-name="SSW deploy SA"

# WIF から SA への impersonation 許可
gcloud iam service-accounts add-iam-policy-binding \
  ssw-deploy@$PROJECT_ID.iam.gserviceaccount.com \
  --role=roles/iam.workloadIdentityUser \
  --member="principalSet://iam.googleapis.com/projects/$(gcloud projects describe $PROJECT_ID --format='value(projectNumber)')/locations/global/workloadIdentityPools/github/attribute.repository/YOUR_GH_ORG/ssw-public"

# ssw-deploy SA の権限
for role in roles/run.admin roles/cloudbuild.builds.editor \
            roles/artifactregistry.writer roles/iam.serviceAccountUser; do
  gcloud projects add-iam-policy-binding $PROJECT_ID \
    --member="serviceAccount:ssw-deploy@$PROJECT_ID.iam.gserviceaccount.com" \
    --role=$role
done
```

GitHub repo の Settings > Secrets に登録:
- `WIF_PROVIDER`: `projects/<PROJECT_NUMBER>/locations/global/workloadIdentityPools/github/providers/github-oidc`
- `PROJECT_ID`: `ssw-public-prod`

### 3. Runtime Service Account (BYOSA — v2 §8.2)

```bash
gcloud iam service-accounts create ssw-runtime \
  --display-name="SSW runtime (BYOSA)"

# Discovery Engine viewer (data store 限定 — IAM Conditions で絞る)
gcloud projects add-iam-policy-binding $PROJECT_ID \
  --member="serviceAccount:ssw-runtime@$PROJECT_ID.iam.gserviceaccount.com" \
  --role=roles/discoveryengine.viewer

gcloud projects add-iam-policy-binding $PROJECT_ID \
  --member="serviceAccount:ssw-runtime@$PROJECT_ID.iam.gserviceaccount.com" \
  --role=roles/dlp.user

gcloud projects add-iam-policy-binding $PROJECT_ID \
  --member="serviceAccount:ssw-runtime@$PROJECT_ID.iam.gserviceaccount.com" \
  --role=roles/secretmanager.secretAccessor

gcloud projects add-iam-policy-binding $PROJECT_ID \
  --member="serviceAccount:ssw-runtime@$PROJECT_ID.iam.gserviceaccount.com" \
  --role=roles/cloudtrace.agent

gcloud projects add-iam-policy-binding $PROJECT_ID \
  --member="serviceAccount:ssw-runtime@$PROJECT_ID.iam.gserviceaccount.com" \
  --role=roles/logging.logWriter
```

絶対に Editor / Owner / project-wide 権限は付けない。

### 4. Artifact Registry

```bash
gcloud artifacts repositories create ssw-images \
  --repository-format=docker \
  --location=$REGION \
  --description="SSW MCP server container images"
```

## Terraform 適用 (Sprint 3)

```bash
cd infra/terraform/envs/prod
terraform init
terraform plan -out=plan.tfplan
# diff を必ず人間がレビュー
terraform apply plan.tfplan
```

Terraform で作る対象:
- VPC + Serverless VPC Access connector + Cloud NAT (v3 §23.2)
- Cloud Run service (BYOSA bind, max-instances=20, vpc-egress=all-traffic)
- Cloud Armor security policy (rate limit + reCAPTCHA WAF)
- Logging buckets (retention + Bucket Lock for security logs)
- Vertex AI Search data stores (visa_legal, visa_faq, visa_secondary)
- Secret Manager secrets (volume mount target)

## デプロイ実行

GitHub Actions の `deploy` job が main branch push 時に自動実行:

```yaml
# .github/workflows/ci.yml の deploy job 抜粋
- uses: google-github-actions/auth@v2
  with:
    workload_identity_provider: ${{ secrets.WIF_PROVIDER }}
    service_account: ssw-deploy@${{ secrets.PROJECT_ID }}.iam.gserviceaccount.com
- run: |
    gcloud builds submit --config cloudbuild.yaml \
      --substitutions=_REGION=asia-northeast1
```

## デプロイ後検証

```bash
# 公開 URL 取得
gcloud run services describe ssw-mcp --format='value(status.url)'

# ヘルスチェック
curl -i https://<URL>/healthz

# tools/list smoke test
npx @modelcontextprotocol/inspector --cli https://<URL>/mcp --method tools/list

# Cloud Logging で recent error 確認
gcloud logging read 'resource.type="cloud_run_revision" severity>=ERROR' \
  --limit=20 --format=json
```

## ロールバック手順

```bash
# 直前 revision に traffic 100% を戻す
gcloud run services update-traffic ssw-mcp \
  --to-revisions=<PREV_REVISION>=100
```

## チェックリスト

- [ ] Cloud Run service が公開 URL を返す
- [ ] /mcp が 200 + valid MCP JSON を返す
- [ ] tools/list で 3 tool 揃う
- [ ] Cloud Armor が rate limit を発火 (curl で 100 リクエスト/秒テスト)
- [ ] Cloud Logging に PII 文字列が入っていない (grep で確認)
- [ ] BYOSA 確認: `gcloud run services describe ... --format='value(spec.template.spec.serviceAccountName)'` が `ssw-runtime@...`
- [ ] Vertex AI Search data store が 50+ 文書取り込み済